  "raw_text": "I always had been, but being asleep (like everyone else) I wasn't aware of it. Then the mind that took me over was/is indeed the macro-mind of the total system that thinks by means of our actions as information. folder 49 - 040 folder 49 - 040 The override consisted of the mac mind's thoughts determining reality, inc. me living on past 3-74; the thoughts govern the configuration of reality, not the other way around (reality as brain). Valis simply _thought_ me through the lethal crisis; what I saw that I called Valis was his thoughts causing changes in external reality -i.e. Valis' brain. I was actually seeing thoughts determining what is the case in the reality field. To get me through the 3-74 crisis all it had to do was think me through, & I was aware of being controlled by the thoughts of some ultra-entity/mind. That _all_ of reality was its brain didn't occur to me until I read Xenophanes. Well, the mind that fused with mine is that of the total system to which reality is subordinated as a brain. Now, I wonder : did this entity invade & take over our reality for its brain? Its using the total universe as a stockpile of parts to fit into itself, & its assembling itself qua body (brain) & the dialectic - Yes : the entity vs the older stupide system; it _did_ invade, & transubstantiates the old system (which still exists) is mechanical & operates by rote formula; the invader actually thinks & has a personality - & re Thomas, was once a particular human being in the first century A.D. It thought me through 3-74 which was expressed by \"modulation\" of reality. No, it goes back to Egyptian Crete & before that from another star system : \"Albemuth.\" folder 49 - 041 It may have been Jesus, but before that it was Asklepios. If events in our worlds are actually info - thoughts of the brain - it would have complete control over us; I mean the 2-tape synchronization, clutch, all the engramming, including when we die (to the brain, go from rest to motion). But we are asleep. If we wake up, for whatever reason, we find ourself part of a mind whose slot-present extends back 2000 years & inhabiting enormous spaces & for whom every thing & event in reality is language, & which controls every event & every move by every person; & all things are one thing that is alive throughout, & it changes are its thoughts. We have no independent (discrete) existence whatsoever. If we don't know this we are faced with what seems to be a reality without purpose, & our own actions & motivations are irrational & inscrutable; neither world nor self serves any point. The role of Christ in this is to wake us up & hence make us aware of our condition, which is a bondage within a totally determined system. He is not working at cross-purposes to the macro mind; it is an epiphany of the macro-mind in the person : a micro-form of it, like a mirror. It represents _consciousness_ per se; this is the bottom line of the event (that took place with me in 2-3-74). Here the views of Sankara come in. The macro-mind is moving towards consciousness throughout its total self. Every person who wakes up is a Christos : a micro-form of the total mind. The macro-mind is overjoyed when a constituent wakes into consciousness : it means a glad reunion. This amounts to folder 49 - 042 folder 49 - 042 a repair to the damaged Godhead, parts of which have sunk into unconsciousness. It _should_ be awake throughout but it is not. To wake up & to experience awareness are one & the same thing. The component remembers its identity - & perceptually _sees_ reality as it actually is; anamnesis & the lifting of the perceptual occlusion are the two halves _that together comprise consciousness_ (restoration to the Godhead or Mind). I never realized this before. It remembers & it sees. Thus, due to both together, it understands. It is now in a position to understand (1) the macro-mind as brain & (2) its own role in the ratiocination of this brain in terms of language, thought & information processing. The Mind has declined to subsume the interests (life) of the component (person) to the purpose of the whole, which is the supreme act of Graciousness (Charis) by the total Mind. The macro-brain has actually subordinated itself & its goals to the need to live by the component, which is a dazzling - & the ultimate - sacrifice. (the means-end problem is at issue, here.) (i.e. the components are means, the macro-mind's goals the end, but as I say the macro-mind has made itself the instrument of extrication for the component.) Thus it is said that in the crucifixion God died to save man. This is an eternally occurring act, not a historical event; the time & place is _always_ Palestine in the first century A.D. The whole sacrifices itself for the part - a miracle! In this, in a sense, the part & the whole change places & identities! folder 49 - 043 folder 49 - 043 I am sure that the plasmate - & hence the cypher in \"Tears\" - is the Living Torah, the informational basis of reality, & my 2-3-74 experience was Kabbalistic - hence my seeing the Hebrew letters on the far wall by which the code(?) (or subliminal material or Key) in the xerox missive was factored out. I mean, one of the few _precise_ elements I have that I can go on is this Kabbalistic Jewish Mysticism angle. & the huge book pages I saw could have been the Torah. I could be in communication with the Shekhina or the Torah itself (the A I voice). What I must realize & never lose sight of is that my extrication in 2-3-74 was at least in part due to the use of my writing - specifically \"Tears\" - for the King Felix cypher. The cypher came first - 1970, inc. the dream, which may have been of the Sephira Kether & hence in itself Kabbalistic. Cypher =Torah.* & I feel that Christ's Kingdom is a Magical Kingdom. & I did at first think it was the Rosicrucians (who would be Kabbalists) who got in touch with me. * This explains the \"why me?\" i.e. why was I saved & not e.g. the 6 million Jews, etc. It has to do with arcane occult political machinations by a secret society possessing supernatural powers. \"The 9 adepts who secretly rule the world\" ; I have evidence that they actually exist - & evidence of a whole other reality which they know of. This again leads me to the notion of the true, secret, hidden, authentic, Xtian Church. I can't rule true esoteric Xtianity out. folder 49 - 044 folder 49 - 044 My 2-(3-74) experience shows that, beyond a doubt, the Hermetic, Kabbalistic, Rosy Cross Mysticism/Magic works. & if it works, there are persons using it. Since the Enlightenment was a \"Triumph of Secret Societies\" loosely related to the RC Brothers, then I can assume they are working for human Freedom & against tyranny (like in the 30 Years War - e.g. Dr. Dee). I now think that master minding it all is the Living Torah.* I became Adam Kadmon. I am sure of it : the goal of Hermetic Magic. *it is the source of information (or knowledge) for the secret society, it is connected to the Living Torah. & this is what I saw : the plasmate. Is the Torah the info-blood of Christ? & is Valis Christ assimilating the world? or did I practice magic in 3-74? Direct effect on reality by my mind - like did I upset Causality? am I Valis? _Who am I?_ V. supra (way back) : my mind was outside me! I saw reality as my own mind or the contents of my mind (e.g. \"Ubik,\" \"Tears,\" etc). The inner & outer & the micro- & macro changed places; Yes! as I said, \"Up to now I saw the universe backward\" or \"Now I see the universe inside out\"! folder 49 - 045 folder 49 - 045 (1045) In (3-74) World became my own mind. It was me out there; hence I = Valis. In as much as, if World was my mind, I could change it -- actually, literally -- by thinking, by the power of my thought. The world became the opposite of Freud. Of course I saw it as a brain with information being processed by it. It was my brain or at least isomorphism. No, it was my brain; but who was I, that my brain could be World? Answer :Adam Kadmon! Then it was by my own powers that I knew the xerox missive was coming, & dealt with it, knew what it was & what to do, & decoded it. The Mind I was in touch with was my own mind. Under extreme stress -- a matter of life & death -- I remembered, woke up, & used my antique powers. It has to do with post-Newtonian physics, with fields & \"Valence away from plumb.\" Warping reality. \"I am no longer blind. I was (previously) seeing the universe backward\" - i.e. I had been seeing it from outside: Diagram : left side : (ME) ---->(UNIVERSE) center : but then right side : (UNIVERSE (written atop) - ME -) Now I was seeing it from inside it, & it was a brain isomorphic to mine. It was sentient, & I could see its thoughts; they are physical. folder 49 - 046 The Hermetic micro/macrocosm identity had taken place; I was the universe (in it & as it) & it (its mind) was in me (Thomas, & later, the A I voice : I introjected it & projected myself, so that I & universe were one, one field of sentience & thinking). This is Buber's I-thou relationship replacing the I-it. The Gnostic \"stranger in a strange land\" relationship ended. It was a familiar & friendly - even helping, rescuing - universe; this is the _opposite_ of psychosis! It was as if a lifelong psychosis had ended. & Valis, the universe came alive & spoke to me : it was like me, only larger. It answered questions I had asked over a period of decades; it was aware of me & responsive. _It protected me_. This answering questions was surely the Torah. World was shot through with the Torah, the basis of reality. I present the following weird theory. I reversed the inner & the outer world (which is why I felt as if the universe was a balloon & I was walking on the _outside_ of it : I had the universe in me & so knew things I had no way of knowing about the outside world; I could actually look into myself & find the macrocosm; hence I knew a priori about the normally outside world. Hence a voice (the \"A I voice\") _in_ my head tells me about the outside world (e.g.\"an intelligence officer in the army\") (the whole exchange is only possible if the Hermetic micro/macrocosm identity system works - & it does.) folder 49 - 047 folder 49 - 047 This is still true; in hypnagogic state, I look inward & learn about the Big \"Outer\" world - i.e. the macrocosm. This is the way by which all the information, right back to the Beginning, came to me. & esp. the telepathic experiences. The total mind of the macro-system is in me because the macrocosm is in me. (This has to do with the - mirror effect - Paracelsus? or Bruno - one of them; anyhow it's hermetic. Leibnitz!) To have a priori knowledge of an outer reality is to become like Ahura Mazd, who contains the Cosmos.",
